{"tid":1835232,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[1Q題］連登邊隻吉祥物最難感染武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-01-22T18:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:46:09.000Z","uid":256077,"like":132,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6107c98d353cd0772756fe790a83473ff30702","tid":1835232,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:44:48.000Z","msg":"答案係：腦魔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢帶既係外科手術口罩<br />\n仲要不停咁換新口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢最難感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次係：連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢都係帶外科手術口罩<br />\n但係佢無換口罩<br />\n而且仲攞住支疫苗搖來搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢係第二難感染<br />\n<br />\n最尾係：連豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢係帶黑口罩<br />\n防護性冇外科手術口罩咁好<br />\n仲係成日又除低又戴番<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢係最容易感染"},{"pid":"3b95bcda2d26f3b93bfdfe6e472cbc1d1cfe7103","tid":1835232,"uid":256077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T18:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f99b7fedbe9e50df6